<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最近啊，<delay8 />
经常有人说<delay20 />
我的眼神变凶恶了<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前一阵子<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" />也跟我说，<delay8 />
我的目光太过锐利，<delay20 />
非常吓人。
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />毕竟晚上外出巡逻，<delay8 />
还挺累人的啊，<delay20 />
也许是因为这个原因吧。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay8 />如果我不巡逻的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那要由谁来守护
这座<tag a="110" b="32" />的和平啊？！
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这活儿<delay8 />
还是得要我来做才行。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 04 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />你没事吧？！<delay20 />
可不能勉强自己！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_3 arg="8" />我想到了，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay20 /><20_3 arg="4" />
<20_2 arg="6" />是为了这样辛苦付出的<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />哦。<pageBreak />我们是不是应该<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也帮他<delay8 />一些忙呢？！</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">交给我吧！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那有点……</message>
	<message label="002_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">好可怕<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样才对嘛～！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
我们一起努力吧～！
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />对了！<delay8 /><20_2 arg="7" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay frames="40" /><20_2 arg="5" />
<20_2 arg="8" />还有<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你们听说最近的传闻了吗？
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说是这两天一到晚上，<delay20 />
就有一个眼睛闪闪发光的危险人物<delay8 />
在整个<tag a="110" b="32" />上四处游荡呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还有这回事<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过我倒是<delay8 />
没有遇见过那种家伙啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="6" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 /><20_2 arg="3" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要是看见形迹可疑的人物，就放声大喊吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我会立马赶到<delay8 />制服那种家伙的！</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～？<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
你难道是觉得害怕吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你们<delay8 />不必勉强，<delay frames="40" />
这种事情由我负责就好！</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的眼神<delay20 />
一直就是这么凶恶的啦～<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但他其实是个好人哦！
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />对了对了，<delay8 />说起晚上，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="2" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你们听过这个消息吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说是有个眼睛闪闪发光的可怕人物<delay8 />
在这个<tag a="110" b="32" />上到处游荡呢！<delay40 />
是不是超～级恐怖的？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还有这回事<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
不过我倒是<delay8 />
没有遇见过那种家伙啊？
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_3 arg="6" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay frames="40" />
你这人挺胆小的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是发生了什么事，<delay8 />记得立刻呼叫我！
就由我亲自出马，<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把那种行迹可疑的家伙
给痛扁一顿吧！<anim id="Clapping" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">对了，<delay8 />最近在年轻人之间，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />流行把上衣披在肩上吗？</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～<delay8 />你不知道吗？<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样披在肩膀上，<delay8 />
能给人一种自然轻松的感觉！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比直接穿起来更能体现风格，<delay8 />
也更时尚哦？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自、<delay8 />自然轻松的感觉<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay20 />
我实在是无法理解
时下这些年轻人的想法啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那不就跟<delay8 />当年流行过的<delay8 />
老式穿法一模一样吗！</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />你对时尚是真的
没有什么敏感度呀……<10_4 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那这个，<delay8 />你知道吗？</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现在<delay8 />有一种潮流，<delay8 />
就是跟着最时尚的曲子<delay8 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跳又帅又可爱的舞蹈哦～！<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而我的招牌动作就是这个！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="10" b="12" /><size value="150" />闪亮亮～！<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最后露出超级可爱的笑容，
结束整个舞蹈！<delay20 />
就像这种感觉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我不太能理解，<delay20 />
不过只要你觉得开心，<delay8 />
就没什么问题了吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="10" b="12" /><size value="150" />华丽丽～！<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让大家感受到我的可爱之后，<delay8 />
再用一个酷酷的动作收尾！<delay20 />
就像这种感觉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现在可是很流行<delay8 />
彩虹的配色哦！<pageBreak />因为七色彩虹<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很有童话感，
而且也超～级可爱的呀～<delay20 />
忍不住就会想拍上两张照片了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />噢！<delay8 />这个观点<delay20 />
我倒是能够理解啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也很喜欢彩虹哦！<delay20 />
毕竟彩虹是象征幸运的东西嘛。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是看着<delay8 />就感觉心情愉快啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />听好咯！<delay20 />
“可爱”这种形容词<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
对男人来说<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可不是赞美之词啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～<delay8 />为什么？！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay8 />你<delay8 />看起来就很可怕，<delay8 />
说话也很粗暴……<anim id="Angry" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />但你那个“<tag a="110" b="5" />”的口头禅<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超～级可爱的，有一股反差萌啊！<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />从现在开始我也来<delay8 />
模仿你的口头禅吧～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什么？！<delay20 />
你说我的口头禅<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />很、很可爱？！<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就<delay8 />饶了我吧！<delay20 />
我可不是因为这种原因
才用这个口头禅的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果我用起来，<delay8 />说不定会更加可爱～！<delay20 />
这算不算是又向着偶像<delay8 />
前进了一步呢？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><10_4 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />行了行了，<delay8 />我知道啦！<delay20 />
就随你喜欢吧！</message>
</msbt>